											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The player turns from the skies back to the bay. They walk out to the docks to watch the dying rays of the sun ripple across the water.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;We could start similar to the Dragon's Arrive Stage from END_BrainBattle_CombatOver, but it's probably simpler to cut to a neutral shot and walk down to the docks." />
